	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />My monitor is a widescreen but the only widescreen setting it supports is 1360x768. but that makes everything a bit too small for me.
<br />
<br />Is there a way I can keep it set to that and yet have everything display as if its set lower?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
