	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />What kind of monitor is it? Most 1360x768 pixel widescreens that I've seen are TVs, and TVs tend to be big. Or is your monitor a 1024x600 panel in a netbook?
<br />
<br />Does zooming in a web page also zoom in objects rendered by plug-ins (e.g. SWF, Java)?
<br />
<br />As for the fuzziness, try Display Properties &gt; Appearance &gt; Effects and see if playing with the ClearType setting does anything.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


