		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I actually found a real solution for this wile I was screwing around tonight.
<br />
<br />Under Display Properties in the settings tad, click the advanced button, then under Display increase the DPI settings. this combined with used large icons and extra large text seems to work ok although still flawed

		

